divs: Sighting Detailsi was driving home from work on bi-pass from goshen to south bend, in. i saw them to my left in the distance about 5 minutes from the 331 exit . There was a plane , that was going over the road back and forth , looked like it was crop dusting, but it wasn't. It looked like someone was practicing flying, but going back and forth over the road. Saw this about 2 minutes after ufo sightings.
Summary: 5 black objects , that were fast, smaller then a plane flew through air, like birds migrating in a group. flew straight, and fast, were gone within a minute.
